---
title: Thai Glazed Duck Breast with Ginger-Garlic Rice & Broccolini
description: Elegant and impressive yet without all the fuss! Beautifully glazed duck breast with soy broccolini and aromatic ginger-garlic rice make for a fantastic special occasion dinner that's sure to make jaws drop the moment you serve up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-spiced-duck-breast-4b7ae799.jpg
